<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>傍晚，潘校长和其他的教师们到达了美罗城格兰德酒店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个叫做思维普斯的神秘男人邀请他们去参加一个特别的会议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘也许他要给学校捐些款。’潘校长想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎你们。”思维普斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请拿一个胸针。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘校长把一个星星模样的胸针别在了夹克上面，然后坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在。”思维普斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我来告诉你们，为什么会邀请你们来到这里……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是一个美丽的秋天早晨，罗西和她的朋友们正向学校走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天气一直都是这样就好了。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们班下周组织一起去动物园。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经等不及要去看蛇了。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我担心我们去不了。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我妈妈告诉我，我们学校现在很需要钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许去动物园的活动会被取消。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就太糟糕了！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要做点什么来帮助我们的学校。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能做什么呢？”玛拉问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们又没有钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许火箭女孩儿可以帮忙。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可不这么认为。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿也没有钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有什么是火箭女孩儿办不到的。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是最棒的超级英雄！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，罗西和她的朋友们到达了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向停车场望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师们的车怎么都不在？”她自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“学生们，欢迎你们！”一个站在学校门口的男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在发放星星模样的胸针。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是思维普斯先生，是你们的代理校长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘校长……嗯……在忙别的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西怀疑地看着思维普斯先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个代理校长有些奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的！谢谢您给我这个胸针。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯先生把一个胸针递给了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是你的，小姑娘。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。”罗西小心翼翼地看着胸针说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快，把它带上。”思维普斯先生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西听到了她手表的响声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把胸针放进了口袋里面，然后快速地离开了学校大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西按下手表的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”她说，“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有麻烦了，火箭女孩儿。”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘校长失踪了，我想让你查查看她发生了什么事儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看思维普斯先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要担心。”罗西说，“我会找到潘校长的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>